1. *Vjeruj* da ćeš uspjeti! (Believe that you will succeed!)
2. On je savršen, ali ja mu *vjerujem* samo na papiru. (He is perfect, but I only trust him on paper.)
3. Ona je toliko mnogo puta prevarila, da je teško *vjerovati* joj. (She has cheated so many times, that it is hard to trust her.)
4. Ova situacija nam govori da ne *vjerujemo* svemu što čujemo. (This situation is telling us not to believe everything that we hear.)
5. Da li ti *vjeruješ* u ono što govoriš? (Do you believe in what you are saying?)